This application demonstrates some of the more complex features of Monkeybars
including use of the transfer and signals.  This application also comes with
a spec for the controller demonstrating how you can easily test your GUI
applications.

Uses the Flickraw library (provided as a gem).

Run with: jruby src/main.rb

The class files were compiled using Netbeans, thus the existence of a build
directory, if using rawr or another compilation tool you will need to adjust
the classpath in manifest.rb to load that location.